'''Commenta in Ciceronis Rhetorica''' is a work written by [[Gaius Marius Victorinus]] in the 4th century AD. It is the sole integral commentary on [[Cicero]]'s ''[[De Inventione]]'' which survived.<ref>{{cite web|title=Commenta in Ciceronis Rhetorica. Accedit incerti auctoris tractatus de attributis personae et negotio. Aims and scope|website=degruyter.com|url=https://www.degruyter.com/view/product/205768|accessdate=29 December 2016}}</ref> A new critical edition has been issued between 2013 and 2015.

